publicwhip.spmotion: *S3M-1938 Patricia Ferguson: Milton Kids DASH Club Premiere of It’s a Wrap!—That the Parliament congratulates the Milton Kids DASH Club on the world premiere of It’s a Wrap!, its first movie; notes the hard work by the staff of the project and the Fablevision film artists who made the project possible, and particularly applauds the young people whose enthusiasm and hard work shone through.
